{
  "texts": [
    "Traditional online learning systems are based on different filtering methods that often rely on user behavior in the face of different sources.",
    "Recommending resources extracted from users with similar behavior often does not have satisfactory results.",
    "Hagemann et al.",
    "20 proposed a personal recommender to help students make informed decisions about their learning path 22.",
    "This study aimed to improve the path of discovery of selected modules by students using a hybrid recommender system explicitly designed to help students better discover available options."
  ]
}